exceptions.exn: Cannot turn inductive Params into an evaluable reference.

exceptions.tactic: intros H1 H2; split; simpl; intros; try omega.

original: unfold Params. intros H1 H2; split; simpl; intros; try omega. destruct H; split. + apply H1. rewrite !elements_iff in *. rewrite H0; auto. + apply H2. rewrite !elements_iff in *. rewrite H0; auto.
